{"tid":1433093,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［全民起義，天滅中共］行動已經完全升級 成為一場反共運動","createTime":"2019-08-08T11:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T02:51:22.000Z","uid":258731,"like":11,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cf907d299f9e9f1bc09ab01121f0cbf846741090","tid":1433093,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:41:33.000Z","msg":"大家記住，大家嘅目標唔係落街撚狗<br />\n<br />\n中共就係想我哋將回歸二十年嚟對施政所有怨氣發洩落狗狗身上，藉此達維穩作用，一定唔可以中計<br />\n<br />\n終極目標：輸出革命，要令中共惡夢成真<br />\n<br />\n手段：仿照毛澤東搞革命思維同方式，叫佢哋叫過嘅口號，以其人之道還治其人之身<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n全民起義，天滅中共<br />\n<br />\n革命無罪，造反有理，打倒共產黨！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n麻煩文宣組幫手製作有關長輩圖，多謝"},{"pid":"b53fc141f71d4a1e7aea057500ac656088ced40f","tid":1433093,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:46:01.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"1b5b1eb057b161b9bb2e090fff24342b65a9a267","tid":1433093,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:46:11.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"2ff0e162a6821554cc2bc02db33d1b9437e1e8f8","tid":1433093,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:46:23.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"fd3c0589a7425a3a693b64fca414eff7268f74b1","tid":1433093,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:46:34.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"6371604a80f7b69a2954b3e8764940cc8ae34488","tid":1433093,"uid":61824,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:47:42.000Z","msg":"智障既鬼 大家唔使睇<br />\n負皮 下一頁"},{"pid":"ac72a0649ef075b1d8f7525ca10f4dd428a2d63c","tid":1433093,"uid":55080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:48:44.000Z","msg":"全民起義，天滅中共<br />\n<br />\n革命無罪，造反有理，打倒共產黨！"},{"pid":"6e6c69366b2ae76fec9d9ddb8e0d906f2d791110","tid":1433093,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:50:07.000Z","msg":"全民起義，天滅